OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian culture minister   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprobed over stolen painting
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An Italian junior culture minister has 
OL,6, been accused of possessing and         
OL,7, exhibiting a stolen 17th Century       
OL,8, painting, which he denies.             
OL,10,FThe latest allegations to hit a member 
OL,11,Fof Italy's government centre on        
OL,12,FVittorio Sgarbi, a renowned art critic.
OL,14,FMr Sgarbi has been put under           
OL,15,Finvestigation for laundering stolen    
OL,16,Fgoods after including the painting in a
OL,17,F2021 exhibition.                       
OL,19,F"The Capture of Saint Peter" was       
OL,20,Freported stolen in 2013.               
